DevOps can be said to be the relationship between Development process and Operation process of building and deploying a product or services.
Most people like to say there is no definitio for devops instead it is a practice. 
Devops engineers are mostly focused on making sure that both the developing stage and operation stage of a product is in sync to aid faster launch and this also helps in fixing bugs along the line as there is all hands on deck. 

In an organization devops are known to be respected as they are mostly in charge of coming up with different meti=hods to make sure that the product beats the competitors and also maiximize their resources
To become a devops engineer you have to learn different tools and akso sysytems,this include both latest and old technologies and can be a lot.
